    <title>MonoXiver： Monocular 3D Object Detection with Bounding Box Denoising in 3D by Perceiver</title>
    <link>http://localhost:1683/Blogs_lovelt/posts/monoxiver--monocular-3d-object-detection-with-bounding-box-denoising-in-3d-by-perceivermonocular-3d-object-detection-with-bounding-box-denoising-in-3d-by-perceiver/</link>
